org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.governanceaction.properties.OpenMetadataPrimitiveDef
public class OpenMetadataPrimitiveDef extends OpenMetadataAttributeTypeDef
OpenMetadataPrimitiveDef supports the definition of a primitive type. This information is managed in the OpenMetadataPrimitiveDefCategory.
